net.objectzoo.ebc

Interface EntryPoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CanStart

    public interface EntryPoint
extends CanStart
    This is a special marker interface that can be used to tag an EBC as the EntryPoint of an application. The start action of the EBC is to be called on application start.
